---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Mikey Somatics | Trauma-Informed Somatic Healing & Wellness">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[680px] overflow-hidden bg-cover bg-center md:bg-[center_42%]" style="background-image: url('/images/hero-main.png');">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.96) 0%, rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.9) 48%, rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.68) 100%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-28 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-cream"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-5">Mikey Alexander, ITP</p>
        <h1 class="max-w-3xl text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.5rem] font-bold leading-tight text-forest mb-7" style="font-family: 'Lora', serif;">
          Somatic Therapy for Stress, Pain, and Trauma
        </h1>
        <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed mb-9">
          Body-based sessions to calm your nervous system, process stored stress, and support lasting emotional balance.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-10">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-forest text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm tracking-wide shadow-lg shadow-forest/10 hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
            Book Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border border-forest/25 bg-cream/60 text-forest px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-cream transition-colors">
            Explore Services
          </a>
        </div>
        <ul class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm text-charcoal/75 list-none">
          <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-forest/10 bg-cream/70 px-4 py-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M8,2 Q13,6 8,14 Q3,6 8,2Z" fill="#7a9e8e" opacity="0.8"/><line x1="8" y1="5" x2="8" y2="12" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="0.5"/></svg>
            Accepting new clients
          </li>
          <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-forest/10 bg-cream/70 px-4 py-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M8,2 Q13,6 8,14 Q3,6 8,2Z" fill="#7a9e8e" opacity="0.8"/><line x1="8" y1="5" x2="8" y2="12" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="0.5"/></svg>
            60-minute appointments
          </li>
          <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-forest/10 bg-cream/70 px-4 py-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M8,2 Q13,6 8,14 Q3,6 8,2Z" fill="#7a9e8e" opacity="0.8"/><line x1="8" y1="5" x2="8" y2="12" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="0.5"/></svg>
            Telehealth available anywhere in the US
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- My Approach -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/nature-polaroid.png" alt="Nature and healing" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-3/4 mx-auto" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">My Approach</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-forest mb-6">Keeping it Simple.</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The world is complex, but healing really comes down to one thing: feeling safe. When your body feels safe, it knows how to release what it's been holding onto. My role is to help you get there.
        </p>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          Through somatic experiencing, internal family systems, and pain reprocessing therapy, we work together to calm your nervous system, process stored stress, and rebuild that sense of safety from the inside out.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modalities -->
  <section class="relative pt-16 pb-6 overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-cream) 0%, var(--color-sand) 50%);">
    <!-- Animated background shapes -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <svg class="absolute w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 1200 800" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
        <circle cx="150" cy="200" r="180" fill="#7a9e8e" opacity="0.04">
          <animate attributeName="cx" values="150;230;150" dur="22s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
          <animate attributeName="cy" values="200;280;200" dur="18s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
        </circle>
        <circle cx="800" cy="300" r="220" fill="#2d4a3e" opacity="0.03">
          <animate attributeName="cx" values="800;720;800" dur="20s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
          <animate attributeName="cy" values="300;220;300" dur="24s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
        </circle>
        <circle cx="500" cy="100" r="160" fill="#c4a882" opacity="0.04">
          <animate attributeName="cx" values="500;580;500" dur="26s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
          <animate attributeName="cy" values="100;180;100" dur="20s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
        </circle>
        <circle cx="1000" cy="500" r="200" fill="#7a9e8e" opacity="0.03">
          <animate attributeName="cx" values="1000;920;1000" dur="19s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
          <animate attributeName="cy" values="500;420;500" dur="23s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
        </circle>
        <circle cx="300" cy="600" r="150" fill="#c4a882" opacity="0.035">
          <animate attributeName="cx" values="300;380;300" dur="24s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
          <animate attributeName="cy" values="600;520;600" dur="17s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
        </circle>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-8">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">Modalities</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-forest">How We Work Together</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-8 fade-card" style="transition-delay:0ms;">
        <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none">
          <!-- Body silhouette with waves -->
          <circle cx="32" cy="14" r="6" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <path d="M22,28 Q27,24 32,26 Q37,24 42,28 L40,50 Q36,52 32,52 Q28,52 24,50 Z" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M18,34 Q25,30 32,34 Q39,30 46,34" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M18,40 Q25,36 32,40 Q39,36 46,40" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M20,46 Q26,42 32,46 Q38,42 44,46" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold mb-2">Somatic Experiencing</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-8 fade-card" style="transition-delay:150ms;">
        <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none">
          <!-- Nerve network - nodes -->
          <circle cx="32" cy="12" r="3" fill="#2d4a3e"/>
          <circle cx="16" cy="24" r="2.5" fill="#2d4a3e"/>
          <circle cx="48" cy="20" r="2.5" fill="#2d4a3e"/>
          <circle cx="24" cy="38" r="3" fill="#2d4a3e"/>
          <circle cx="44" cy="36" r="2.5" fill="#2d4a3e"/>
          <circle cx="10" cy="48" r="2" fill="#7a9e8e"/>
          <circle cx="32" cy="52" r="3" fill="#2d4a3e"/>
          <circle cx="54" cy="50" r="2" fill="#7a9e8e"/>
          <circle cx="38" cy="26" r="2" fill="#7a9e8e"/>
          <!-- Connections -->
          <line x1="32" y1="12" x2="16" y2="24" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="32" y1="12" x2="48" y2="20" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="32" y1="12" x2="38" y2="26" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="0.75"/>
          <line x1="16" y1="24" x2="24" y2="38" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="48" y1="20" x2="44" y2="36" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="48" y1="20" x2="38" y2="26" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="0.75"/>
          <line x1="38" y1="26" x2="44" y2="36" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="0.75"/>
          <line x1="38" y1="26" x2="24" y2="38" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="0.75"/>
          <line x1="24" y1="38" x2="10" y2="48" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="24" y1="38" x2="32" y2="52" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="44" y1="36" x2="32" y2="52" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="44" y1="36" x2="54" y2="50" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="16" y1="24" x2="10" y2="48" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="0.75" opacity="0.5"/>
          <line x1="48" y1="20" x2="54" y2="50" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="0.75" opacity="0.5"/>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold mb-2">Pain Reprocessing</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-8 fade-card" style="transition-delay:300ms;">
        <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none">
          <!-- Flowing breath/wind lines -->
          <path d="M8,18 Q20,14 32,18 Q44,22 56,18" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M12,28 Q24,24 36,28 Q48,32 58,26" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M6,38 Q18,34 30,38 Q42,42 54,36" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M14,48 Q26,44 38,48 Q50,52 60,46" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold mb-2">Breathwork</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-8 fade-card" style="transition-delay:450ms;">
        <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none">
          <!-- Connected circles for parts/IFS -->
          <circle cx="32" cy="16" r="8" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <circle cx="18" cy="42" r="8" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <circle cx="46" cy="42" r="8" stroke="#2d4a3e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="28" y1="23" x2="21" y2="35" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="36" y1="23" x2="43" y2="35" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="26" y1="42" x2="38" y2="42" stroke="#7a9e8e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="32" cy="16" r="3" fill="#c4a882" opacity="0.4"/>
          <circle cx="18" cy="42" r="3" fill="#c4a882" opacity="0.4"/>
          <circle cx="46" cy="42" r="3" fill="#c4a882" opacity="0.4"/>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold mb-2">Parts Work (IFS)</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trauma Informed Care -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/peaceful-room.png" alt="Peaceful room for somatic healing" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-3/4 mx-auto" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">Trauma Informed Care</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-forest mb-6">A Safe Space for You</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          My role is to be a compassionate guide as you navigate your path to recovery. Together, we create a space where you can explore your experiences at your own pace, without pressure or judgment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          I honor your unique history and identity. Trauma impacts the mind, body, and relationships in profound ways. This approach fosters empowerment and connection, helping you reconnect with yourself and build lasting resilience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Remote Care -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-10 bg-forest text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">Remote Care</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light mb-6">Sessions From Anywhere</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I conduct sessions virtually and find that many clients enjoy the familiarity and safety of their own homes. I also recognize that this isn't always the case for everyone.
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        I'm based in Brooklyn and while I don't have a dedicated studio, I'm happy to meet in person at a safe, comfortable space that works for you.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-forest px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-sand transition-colors font-medium">
        Book Free Consult
      </a>
      <div class="border-t border-white/20 mt-10 max-w-md mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        entry.target.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'translate-y-8');
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.2 });

  document.querySelectorAll('.fade-card').forEach(card => observer.observe(card));
</script>

</Layout>
